      <title>Facets an array of words rather than sentences</title>
      <link>http://projects.ez.no/ezfsolrdocumentfieldobjectrelation/forum/general/facets_an_array_of_words_rather_than_sentences</link>
      <description>When I use an object relations field as a facet, the facets are separated at the spaces so I get an array of words instead of names of the related objects.  For example:&#13;
&#13;
"This is a related object name" gets listed as: &#13;
&#13;
"This"&#13;
"is"&#13;
"a"&#13;
"related"&#13;
"object"&#13;
"name"&#13;
&#13;
I think this has something to do with the content being indexed as text "_t" rather than string "_s", but I don't know how to fix it.  Any guidance would be much appreciated!&#13;
&#13;
Thanks,&#13;
&#13;
Fraser&#13;
</description>
