      <description>Thanks for this great contribution, it's really useful!  I have one problem: it seems to work in some cases and not others.  For example I have two identical object relations attributes in two different classes and the faceting and filtering works in one and not the other.  For some reason one is properly indexed as string and the other as text:  &#13;
&#13;
